{"sn2.7:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.7 ","sn2.7:0.2":"1. Pathamavagga ","sn2.7:0.3":"Pancalacandasutta ","sn2.7:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn2.7:1.2":"Ekamantam thito kho pancalacando devaputto bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","sn2.7:2.1":"“Sambadhe vata okasam, ","sn2.7:2.2":"Avindi bhurimedhaso; ","sn2.7:2.3":"Yo jhanamabujjhi buddho, ","sn2.7:2.4":"Patilinanisabho muni”ti. ","sn2.7:3.1":"“Sambadhe vapi vindanti, ","sn2.7:3.2":"(pancalacandati bhagava) ","sn2.7:3.3":"Dhammam nibbanapattiya; ","sn2.7:3.4":"Ye satim paccalatthamsu, ","sn2.7:3.5":"Samma te susamahita”ti. "}